Edward Vieira, 25, with a .25-caliber pistol during a confrontation in Granada 
Hills after the Palmdale brothers traded insults with five teen-agers, 
including Bellinger. 
</P>
<P>
"This kid is falling apart," Vicary -- called by Bellinger's attorney -- 
testified in the fitness hearing in Pasadena Juvenile Court. "That is why you 
see him doing something so stupid -- something really out of character for 
him." 
